The Vital Football Fantasy Football will be live on August 3 giving members plenty of time before the new season kicks off to join up, select a team of Premiership players and show the 'real' managers exactly how it is done! Our game will be available to all comers including members of Vital Football as well as access for William Hill customers. You'll be able to compete against members from across the Vital Network, fellow members on your team site, as well as friends and colleagues as you can set up your own leagues to prove you are the best manager out there!
